Package: wps-read-aloud-zhangjingyao
Version: 1.0.14
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: zhangjingyao <zhangjingyao@example.invalid>
Description: Offline read-aloud WPS JS add-in for Kylin ARM64
 Developer: zhangjingyao. Release date: 20260516.
 Provides a WPS JS add-in and local offline TTS daemon. The daemon listens
 only on 127.0.0.1 and uses a bundled Sherpa-onnx VITS fanchen-C Chinese
 model for clear offline read-aloud with lightweight English preprocessing.
